text: Desmiphora compacta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1942. It is known from Brazil and Paraguay.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora compacta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1942
title: Desmiphora compacta
